title: Average Rain Per Day, Rain Station in Africa, Fews.net
name: Average Rain Per Day, Rain Station in Africa, Fews.net
description:
This is a csv of average rain per day data for rain stations in 13 African countries. This data comes from Fews.net and can be found at http://earlywarning.usgs.gov/adds/xceltheme.php?hidformsubmit=1. For each station there are three years present in the data. Below are the specific years available for each station, which could not be listened out in the actual dataset. Please refer to this for actual years. 

Burkina Faso- 2002, 2000, 1995
Sudan- 2000, 1995, no year
Somalia-1998, no year, no year
Mozambique-2002, 2000, 1995
Rwanda-2001, 2000, no year
Uganda-2002, 2000, 1995
Zimbabwe-1999, 1996, no year
Zambia-2002, 2000, 1996
Tanzania-2001, 2000, no year
Chad-2003, 2000, 1995
Niger-2003, 2000, 1995
Malawi-2001, 1995, no year
Kenya-2003, 2000, no year
